# AttachLink Design Specification

Complete visual design documentation for the AttachLink platform, covering all pages in both light and dark modes.

---

## Color Palette

### Light Mode

- **Primary Blue**: `#4f67eb` (Main brand color)
- **Primary Hover**: `#3d52d4` (Darker blue for hover states)
- **Primary Light**: `#e8ebfa` (Light blue for backgrounds)
- **Secondary**: `#eff1fc` (Light gray-blue)
- **Background**: `#ffffff` (Pure white)
- **Foreground**: `#1a1a1a` (Nearly black text)
- **Card Background**: `#ffffff` (White cards)
- **Border**: `#e5e7eb` (Light gray borders)
- **Text Gray**: `#6b7280` (Muted text)
- **Text Dark**: `#111827` (Primary text)
- **Success**: `#10b981` (Green for success states)
- **Danger**: `#ef4444` (Red for errors/rejected)
- **Warning**: `#f59e0b` (Orange for warnings)

### Dark Mode

- **Primary Blue**: `#7c90f2` (Lighter blue for dark backgrounds)
- **Primary Hover**: `#97a7f5` (Even lighter for hover)
- **Primary Light**: `#2a3250` (Dark blue-tinted background)
- **Secondary**: `#2a3250` (Dark blue-gray)
- **Background**: `#0f111a` (Very dark blue-black)
- **Foreground**: `#f0f0f0` (Off-white text)
- **Card Background**: `#1a1d2e` (Dark blue-tinted cards)
- **Border**: `#2d3448` (Darker borders)
- **Text Gray**: `#9ca3af` (Lighter muted text)
- **Text Dark**: `#f0f0f0` (Primary text in dark mode)

